cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you cite or implement AIISP-1, please reference this draft."
title: "AIISP-1: The Artificial Intelligence Inference Standards Protocol"
abstract: >
  AIISP-1 specifies a minimal, transport-agnostic, opt-in HTTP standard for
  declaring and settling the energy, environmental, and human-attribution
  components of a single Large Language Model inference request.
